&lt;a href="https://gbdev.gg8.se/wiki/articles/Video_Display#VRAM_Sprite_Attribute_Table_.28OAM.29"&gt;https://gbdev.gg8.se/wiki/articles/Video_Display#VRAM_Sprite_Attribute_Table_.28OAM.29&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
